00:04:30.271 --> 00:04:32.270
Amylase begins the process of breaking down 

00:04:32.484 --> 00:04:34.480
complex carbohydrates, called polysaccharides.

00:04:34.157 --> 00:04:36.160
These are mostly starches. 

00:04:40.559 --> 00:04:42.560
